{
  "stem": "4113.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The other soldiers grabbed him and pulled him back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then he threatened me that he was going to report me to the Gestapo, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The others pulled him back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And a cousin of mine, a half-cousin of mine who used to work with us, Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Heller, Moshe Heller, he pulled me away, gave me a hit sort of, you know, and things calmed down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The only time that I personally have experienced any animosity from German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we worked for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And things were relatively quiet until-- here and there in 1940, '41, there would be a sporadic shooting of a Jew here, a Jew there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Supposedly he didn't wear-- they caught him not wearing this, his armband, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it was relatively quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Then came 1941.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- we knew that something was going on, because for a few weeks prior to the invasion of the Soviet Union-- Operation Barbarossa, that was the code name for the invasion of the Soviet Union-- there was lots of traffic going on.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were extremely busy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And you already saw slogans on the German trucks, like the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That means the Russian pig is asking what isn't his.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That was a reference made that the Soviets wanted Romania, you know, Bukovina, and all of these countries, the Baltic countries and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew, all of a sudden, they're not kissing each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before that, they, were lovey-bovey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden they hate each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was lots of traffic going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The air base, in particularly-- in particular, was extremely busy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Planes continually getting up, coming all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was busy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, the war broke out, you know, the marching into the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
